      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <article class="mb-10"><h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">How to use this section</h2><p class="mt-3 text-[16px] leading-7 text-neutral-700">Choose a concern to read an overview and see recommended treatments. Your plan is personalized in consultation.</p></article>
